################### AUTHORIZED OPERATION ##############################
#### First login as the admin
##### Define a request variable named admin :
# @name admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auths/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username":"admin",
    "password":"admin"
}

##### 2.1.2 Define a file variable to simplify the access to the token of manager
@adminToken = {{admin.response.body.token}}

### Create a film with the admin token
POST {{baseUrl}}/films
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

{
    "title":"Star Wars: The Phantom Menace (Episode I)",
    "duration": 136,
    "director": "George Lucas",
    "budget": 115,
    "imageUrl":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/4/40/Star_Wars_Phantom_Menace_poster.jpg"
}

### Try to create a film with a parameter missing with the admin token
